Croogo Nodeattachment  plugin
------------------------------
Plugin for binding Croogo attachments to nodes of all
types, except type 'attachment'


How to use
------------------------------
- Log in to admin panel
- Go to Extensions > Plugins page
- Upload the zip file (available here)
- Click on tick/cross icon of 'Nodeattachment' for activating or deactivating the plugin

Notes
------------------------------
- all attachments deleted with this plugin are not deleted
from Croogo nodes table, but only from plugin intrnal assocciation table
- attachments added with this plugin will be added to croogo nodes table
(with type 'attachment') also
- for correct displaying of thumbs, Croogo heleper Image required